{"tid":664978,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國際評級機構　惠譽　中港融合　導致　信貸急增　樓價高企　降香港銀行業評級","createTime":"2018-05-14T14:11:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-03T11:26:51.000Z","uid":47714,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"85849c0dc52c72e1a81f2aa1d29e2d6bf5369237","tid":664978,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T14:11:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.quamnet.com/newscontent.action?articleId=5724420\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.quamnet.com%2Fnewscontent.action%3FarticleId%3D5724420&d=oSQATcPEiOS3RqyQsNV7tYsQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=74f8503b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.quamnet.com/newscontent.action?articleId=5724420</a><br />\n<br />\n評級機構惠譽因應本港與內地的聯繫更為緊密，下調對香港銀行業經營環境的評估，由「A+」下調至「A」、趨勢穩定。<br />\n<br />\n惠譽指出，隨着中港兩地的經濟和金融體系的聯繫日益加深，令本港的信貸快速增長及樓價急升，均對香港帶來風險。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1799192&amp;target=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1799192%26target%3D2&d=oSQATcPEiOS3RqyQsNV7tYsQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=f1d5ea05\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1799192%26target%3D2&h=d4398986\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1799192&amp;target=2</a><br />\n<br />\n評級機構惠譽發表報告，下調香港銀行經營環境評級，由「a+/負面」降至「a/穩定」，反映中港經濟及金融融合加深，對本港銀行帶來風險。惠譽又預期本港銀行向內地企業的貸款額將持續增加，憂慮內地一旦發生金融風險，本港也會受牽連。<br />\n<br />\n　　惠譽表示，香港是最受宏觀風險所影響的全球三個市場之一，本港銀行目前信貸增速加快及樓價高企的原因，很大程度上與內地關連性加深所致。"},{"pid":"5576e4ba398fe99f05589e29a9898cb2c5cc43ca","tid":664978,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T09:37:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13e4fe9d7cdc3d3de6484153bd57b278b1e25ff8","tid":664978,"uid":91633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T09:38:40.000Z","msg":"越痴越衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6112552d172059279bd255a0b47ffecd309a7789","tid":664978,"uid":52817,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T09:50:05.000Z","msg":"由「a+/負面」降至「a/穩定」"},{"pid":"23248d6ab8b8f2300b2d53687daa1c0370c6afc2","tid":664978,"uid":104699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T09:51:02.000Z","msg":"說三道四"},{"pid":"62adba88be635ac392d49495b591b36f7e36ea15","tid":664978,"uid":98163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T10:06:28.000Z","msg":"新聞好似選擇性唔報<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0ac175968f97bae7b25e676c5f78b796d1fe044","tid":664978,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T11:16:10.000Z","msg":"港府有乜回應？"},{"pid":"eaa6a8dbf64677780da6784e8bb66dab1625387f","tid":664978,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T11:18:39.000Z","msg":"樓價唔會跌 係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67743573beae7304028e2454a65444904069b04c","tid":664978,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T11:24:53.000Z","msg":"班高官話有大陸射住怕條撚咩"},{"pid":"2a833faf5113bbac6a0b07463f00507086e98f0b","tid":664978,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T11:25:19.000Z","msg":"仲走緊資架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"701fcc60f2cf63e4d0a5ca1e55f38ab471dec5a3","tid":664978,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0ac175968f97bae7b25e676c5f78b796d1fe044","tid":664978,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T11:16:10.000Z","msg":"港府有乜回應？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T11:26:51.000Z","msg":"吠二聲 <br />\n之後照舊賣港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}